university.botbrewery.desc2:
Brews can come in three forms: 
&bVials&r, which are the most basic with 4 uses; 
&bFlasks&r, which have 6 uses instead of 4; 
&bIncense Sticks&r, which are burned on &6Incense Plates&r and are more like Beacons; 
&bTainted Blood Pendants&r, which are worn as Curios and slowly degrade.
